channel.title: Joltagescape 525 With full elite full dagon hai Dragon claws etc
channel.description:
Ok this one is RS2HD based.
Quited my 525 + 508(<---Wich i released to in the download section.)
cause im working on Boneyard revolution with my team.
This server includes
-Full Elite
-Dclaws With emote click on the Thanksgiving emote :p
-Full Dagon Hai'
-Vesta long
-Full Black Elite
-Skillcape Emotes + Normal emotes.
-Every single Spirit shield.
-Item command for Admin only.
-Most equips wear as they have to wear.
And some more things + Standard RS2HD things.
No anti leech in this one..

Heres the 525 Client to connect to it,(when u run just wait until Listening on port 43594 pops up and your good to connect! http://uppit.com/4YG0RL
Heres the cache Go to your C:/ Drive and make a new folder called cache525 Copy all of the files in the .Rar file in there. http://www.megaupload.com/?d=TGJ2PGCB
Uppit = [url=http://uppit.com/8IR5RG]http://uppit.com/8IR5RG[/url]
2Shared = [url=http://www.2shared.com/file/5017382/fdf654f4/Joltage_525_RS2HD.html]http://www.2shared.com/file/5017382/fdf654f4/Joltage_525_RS2HD.html[/url] (Scroll down Save file to PC)
MegaUpload = [url=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=8LU8KIQD]http://www.megaupload.com/?d=8LU8KIQD[/url]
If u need any other upload site just request it.
Its not much but its something for the people who dont know how to get equip's etc. ~Greetz R.
NOTE: PLEASE IF U DONT EVEN KNOW HOW TO MAKE YOURSELF ADMIN ON A 525 THEN DONT BOTHER WORKING ON ONE. BTW DONT KEEP PMING ME FOR HELP I ONLY CAME HERE TO RELEASE MY SERVER AND MOVE ON.
On Rune-S 3rv my names Get Down for Ramon
Enjoy...
